channel.title: Sedex Professional Team
channel.description:
[center][img]http://img861.imageshack.us/img861/7163/sedexbanner.png[/img][/center] First off I would like to say that this offer is [u][b]only[/b][/u] available to Moparscape, you will not find me asking for a development team anywhere else.
If you are accepted into the development team I would like to say that you will [u][b]not[/b][/u] be paid. You would also not get any rank of owner, admin or mod. You can though have your own commands just for you to show you are a part of staff.
[center][size=16pt] GFX[/size][/center] If you are talented in making GFX, you are going to need a post [b]2[/b] examples in your applications. I need people who can use Photoshop with skill not paint. If you can make videos and GIF's it would also greatly boost your chances of being accepted into the team.
[center][size=16pt]Coders[/size][/center] If you want to be a coder that would like to program the source with me than you will need some special skill to prove it to me, either you will show me your work or I will send you a black source with bad code in it and you will have to fix it via team viewer with me watching. If you are good at clients than your chances of being accepted would be pretty high compared to someone asking to code the source. Lastly we need people who are good at HTML, PHP, Javascript or flash, we have a website but im looking to improve that website by a lot.
[size=12pt]Features of my server[/size] - Perfect woodcutting - Perfect switching - Almost perfect resting - My own custom minigame - My own santa (gone now) - Our own webclient - Frost dragons with animations - Better GWD - FunPK - Domain - New Home - New Skilling Area - Shop that requires referral points to purchase from - Account base of over 1000 accounts created - Many dupe fixes - Our own VPS - Active forum with 600+ posts - Over 1000 working doors - All npcs hit through prayer - Working godbook preaching - Random Events - NPC to reset combat skills - Total Time Played - Chill Area - Theres alot more if you want you can go on the server and see for your self.
[youtube]http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qD3MKZmNJps&feature=plcp&context=C3bd1f65UDOEgsToPDskJDU10W32M4g0dz7zrr0xhm[/youtube] [img]http://img534.imageshack.us/img534/9899/newhome.png[/img] [img]http://img252.imageshack.us/img252/203/minigame.jpg[/img]
If you would like to apply there is no template just write 70+ words why you want to become part of the team, write anything you like post examples and please include contact information Skype, email etc.
